title: Sesame Street Ultimate Disco
description:
This is all 3 of the Sesame Street Disco albums

Sesame Street Fever (1978)

   1. Sesame Street Fever - Robin Gibb, The Count, Grover, Ernie and Cookie Monster
   2. Doin' the Pigeon - Bert and the Girls
   3. Rubber Duckie - Ernie and his Rubber Duckie 
   4. Trash - Robin Gibb
   5. C is for Cookie - Cookie Monster and the Girls
   6. Has Anybody Seen My Dog? - Marty and Grover 


Sesame Disco! (1979)

   1. What Makes Music? - The Entire Cast
   2. Me Lost Me Cookie at the Disco - Cookie Monster and the Girls
   3. The Happiest Street in the World - Big Bird, the Kids and the Girls
   4. Sing - The Girls 
   5. Disco Frog - Kermit the Frog and the Girls
   6. Doin' the Trash - Oscar the Grouch and the Girls
   7. Bein' Green - Kermit the Frog and the Girls
   8. The Happiest Street In The World (Reprise) - Big Bird, the Kids and the Girls 

Solid Steel presents Sesame Street (2003)

   1. C Is for Cookie - Cookie Monster and the Girls (Larry Levan Disco Remix)
   2. Pinball Number Count - The Pointer Sisters (DJ Food)
   1. C Is for Cookie - Cookie Monster and the Girls (Roy Thode Disco Mix)

Enjoy & don't forget to SEED!!!!
